intro_lines = ["Ah! You must be the new carrier. Welcome, name's Bauer your supervisor.", "Now, the last few carriers... they moved on. Quite suddenly. Ha! Don't, erm, read into that.", "Right. Mail around here can be a bit unusual. Addresses, names, things go missing sometimes.", "Your job is to figure out where each letter belongs using whatever's on the envelope.", "Move to a house with A and D, and press Tab to open your bag.", "Drag an envelope onto the slot to deliver it.", "Six deliveries today. Should be simple enough. Mostly. Good luck!"]

